📝 Example Requests
Create Task:

bash

Copy code
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "title": "Complete CRUD app",
    "description": "Build a full CRUD application with Node.js",
    "priority": "high"
  }'
Update Task (PATCH):

bash

Copy code
curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/tasks/YOUR_TASK_ID \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "status": "completed",
    "priority": "medium"
  }'
